title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the Commanders QB Carson Wentz and what his career would've looked like had he not torn his ACL in 2017. HOF NFL Offensive Lineman Anthony Munoz joins us and shares what his strategy would be against Aaron Donald. And Ross Tucker recaps some of his favorite highlights from being at Hall of Fame week. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
